These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, skiing, climbing, rugby
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, dannemann, ritmeester, montecristo
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, aconite, daffodil, marigold
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, goat, goldfish
City: boston, venice, hannover, berlin
 1. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 2. the person who growsmarigold is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person traveling to berlin##2
 3. the owner of the cat is the person traveling to berlin##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 5. the person traveling to boston is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who growsdaffodil##2
 6. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 7. the person traveling to venice is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 8. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 9. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
10. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Sport           | climbing | tennis   | rugby | skiing |
| Cigar   | bongani      | dannemann | ritmeester              | montecristo |
| Flower   | zinnia       | aconite     | marigold               | daffodil    |
| Pet           | dog        | goat     | goldfish           | cat       |
| City     | venice | hannover     | boston                | berlin      |

