.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, comedy, musical, thriller
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, green, orange, fuchsia
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, australian, british
4 different pets are kept: frog, goat, hamster, snake
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, singing, writing
 1. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 2. the american is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 3. the person who likes green is between the person watching musical movies and the owner of the goat##2
 4. the british is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is the person who likes green##1
 6. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 7. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the canadian##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
10. the person who likes orange is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
11. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person watching musical movies##1
12. the person watching spy movies is the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Movie-Genre          | musical       | comedy      | spy      | thriller      |
| Color           | fuchsia | green | orange | blue |
| Nationality   | british          | canadian       | australian            | american      |
| Pet           | frog            | hamster    | goat           | snake       |
| Hobby         | hiking        | reading    | singing         | writing  |

