.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-17::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, grapefruit, tomato, lettuce
House: tower, wooden, farmhouse, futuristic
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, begonia, sunflower, tulip
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, handball, rowing, princeing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, prince, alhambra, aristoff
 1. the tower house is on the right of the person who's sport is princeing##1
 2. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who growsbegonia and the alhambra-smoker##2
 3. the person who growssunflower is between the person eating lettuce and the person eating grapefruit##2
 4. the dannemann-smoker is the wooden house##1
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is the futuristic house##1
 6. the person who growssunflower is the person eating asparagus##1
 7. the aristoff-smoker is the person eating lettuce##1
 8. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
 9. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
10. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who's sport is princeing##1
11. the person who's sport is princeing is between the futuristic house and the aristoff-smoker##2
12. the person who's sport is handball is between the dannemann-smoker and the person eating asparagus##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food      | grapefruit      | asparagus         | lettuce | tomato      |
| House           | futuristic | farmhouse | tower | wooden     |
| Flower   | tulip         | sunflower          | lily  | begonia |
| Sport         | rowing        | princeing  | handball | climbing   |
| Cigar     | prince    | alhambra         | aristoff     | dannemann     |

