.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, mexican, canadian, egyptian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, poppy, daffodil, daisy
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, old-henry, bolivar, aristoff
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, soccer, swimming, tennis
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, november, january, august
 1. the aristoff-smoker is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's birthday is in november##2
 2. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 3. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the mexican##1
 7. the malaysian is the person who growsdaisy##1
 8. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
 9. the egyptian is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
10. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
11. the egyptian is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |   4    |
| Nationality          | malaysian  | egyptian  | mexican  | canadian   |
| Flower   | daisy     | bellflower | daffodil     | poppy |
| Cigar           | bolivar   | aristoff     | old-henry      | bluemaster   |
| Sport         | swimming   | tennis    | lacrosse  | soccer |
| Birthday     | june | august     | november | january |

