.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, italian, chinese, mexican
House: tower, cottage, art-deco, farmhouse
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, designer, paramedic, videographer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, balloon-flower, rose, marigold
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, lilac, grey, lavender
 1. the paramedic is the cottage house##1
 2. the tower house is on the right of the paramedic##1
 3. the italian is between the person who growsmarigold and the videographer##2
 4. the videographer is the person who growsbellflower##1
 5. the spanish is between the italian and the person who likes lavender##2
 6. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 7. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
 8. the tower house is the person who likes grey##1
 9. the italian is on the right of the analyst##1
10. the chinese is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |       4       |
| Nationality      | mexican    | italian     | spanish        | chinese          |
| House         | farmhouse | cottage   | tower        | art-deco |
| Job           | analyst   | paramedic | videographer | designer      |
| Flower   | marigold    | balloon-flower      | bellflower          | rose        |
| Color     | white  | lilac   | grey      | lavender           |

