.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-20::.
House: farmhouse, victorian, craftsman, futuristic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, gospel, salsa
4 different games are played: poker, canasta, whist, bridge
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, july, october, august
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, old-henry, alhambra, pall-mall
 1. the fan of salsa is the person playing canasta##1
 2. the pall-mall-smoker is between the person playing bridge and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 3. the old-henry-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in july and the alhambra-smoker##2
 4. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 7. the victorian house is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 8. the fan of gospel is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
10. the farmhouse house is the person playing poker##1
11. the person playing poker is the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| House         | craftsman  | victorian | futuristic | farmhouse |
| Music-Genre   | salsa      | dubstep   | gospel      | classical    |
| Game   | canasta  | whist | bridge        | poker     |
| Birthday         | april  | july  | october     | august      |
| Cigar     | vegafina | pall-mall      | old-henry   | alhambra       |

 